name: Vibu Export
description: exporting an exclusive range of Flowers,
overview:
Established in the year 1998 as a Sole Proprietorship firm at Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu in India, Vibu Export has carved a distinct position for itself. We are engaged in trading and exporting exclusive range of Curry Leaves, Flowers, Vegetables and Fruits. Our product range primarily includes Drumstick, Green Chills, Snack Gourd, Bitter Gourd, Potatoes, Tomatoes, Curry Leaves, Onion, Cabbage, Coconuts, Banana and Dried Curry Leaves.

Products: Fresh Fruits Fresh Vegetables Fresh Flowers Curry Leaf Plant

Our Quality: Quality-assured production sets us apart from other existing market players. We follow an efficient Total Quality Management (TQM) Program that is established as per the F&B industry’s rules and regulation. Besides, we have established an efficient quality control department that enables us to offer superior quality products to our customers.

Our Team: All the work processes undertaken by our organization is executed by our skilled and experienced pool of professionals. Hailing from varied locales these professionals have clear idea about the existing market trends and years of experience in their domain.

Client Satisfaction: Premier aim of any organization is to render complete client satisfaction that aids in maintain long-term and affable relations with them. We offer our customers with an exclusive variety of fresh vegetable and fruits that are properly packed in safe corrugated boxes to ensure safe transport across national as well as International markets.
